                        Bergherrn</rs>, 2. <rs type="person" ref="pe__konrad_schreiber_QGW_II_I_244"><roleName type="title">hern</roleName> Chunrads, weiln des Polln
                           <roleName type="occ" corresp="pe__berthold_poll_QGW_II_I_121">
                           Schreiber</roleName></rs></rs>.</rs>
